OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,6,Fbest of the sunny spells for East
OL,7,FLothian and the eastern Borders during
OL,8,Fthe morning. The showers could be
OL,9,Fheavy, perhaps the odd rumble of
OL,10,Fthunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely cloudy this evening
OL,13,Fwith showers, some heavy and possibly
OL,14,Fthundery. Most showers dying out
OL,15,Fthrough the night, but a few still
OL,16,Flikely lingering into the early hours.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA mainly dry and partly cloudy
OL,19,Fmorning. Sunny intervals and showers
OL,20,Ffor the afternoon, the best of the
OL,21,Fsunniest conditions on western coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
